300
00:12:16,799 --> 00:12:18,080
When the time comes, put it at the finish line.

301
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,279
Then you'll definitely win the championship.

302
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:20,279
Just run towards me.

303
00:12:20,799 --> 00:12:21,200
Okay.

304
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,279
